About
item.description:
This is a personal blog where I might occasionally post about things that interest me, but is mostly an opportunity to play with data and learn some basic coding.

I enjoy thinking, talking and writing about coffee and messing about with R.

I can be found on Twitter and also LinkedIn.

This blog is built on Hugo using the blogdown R package, and the theme is Hyde.
